<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='605996' id='t-605996'>but without any central coordination.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='608853' id='t-608853'>Every Git system generates this number the same way,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='613342' id='t-613342'>which means this is a signature tied directly</span>
