10:30
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='619834' id='t-619834'>This has the following effect:</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='621770' id='t-621770'>A programmer in Edinburgh and a programmer in Entebbe</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='625448' id='t-625448'>can both get the same -- a copy of the same piece of software.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='629150' id='t-629150'>Each of them can make changes and they can merge them</span>
